trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle navigation events in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerar den metod som hanterar navigering händelser i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The WizardNavigationEventHandler class represents the method that handles the navigation events <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.FinishButtonClick>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.NextButtonClick>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.PreviousButtonClick>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.SideBarButtonClick> for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> control and for controls that inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> control (such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control).
trans-unit.target: Klassen WizardNavigationEventHandler representerar den metod som hanterar händelser för navigering <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.FinishButtonClick>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.NextButtonClick>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.PreviousButtonClick>, och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.SideBarButtonClick>för en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>styr och för kontroller som ärver från den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>kontrollen (som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard>kontroll).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.SideBarButtonClick> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.PreviousButtonClick> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.NextButtonClick> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.FinishButtonClick>

trans-unit.source: When you create a WizardNavigationEventHandler delegate, you identify the method that will handle the event.
trans-unit.target: När du skapar en WizardNavigationEventHandler delegat kan identifiera den metod som hanterar händelsen.

trans-unit.source: To associate the event with your event handler, add an instance of the delegate to the event.
trans-unit.target: Lägga till en instans av delegaten händelsen om du vill associera händelsen med din händelsehanterare.

trans-unit.source: The event handler is called whenever the event occurs, unless you remove the delegate.
trans-unit.target: Händelsehanteraren anropas när händelsen inträffar, om du tar bort delegaten.

trans-unit.source: For more information about event-handler delegates, see [NIB: Events and Delegates](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d98fd58b-fa4f-4598-8378-addf4355a115).
trans-unit.target: Läs mer om händelsehanteraren delegater [NIB: händelser och delegater](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d98fd58b-fa4f-4598-8378-addf4355a115).
